data.text:
"Paula is an original voice both in what she is saying and how she is saying it."

– Peter Gabriel

Cole started as a jazz singer and now returns to pay homage to her first love of jazz and folk. A self-described “mother and human being first,” Cole has a timeless voice that is big, rich and gorgeous, a mind that is intelligent, and a heart that transforms suffering into beauty.
